  ('medical-tech-moex-01958', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下  列關於嗜中性球減少症（neutropenia）的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["血  液中嗜中性球的絕對量可能少於0.2×109/L", "可  能與neutrophil elastase基因突變有關", "可  能會出現在病毒性肝炎感染患者", "可  能會出現在leukemoid reaction患者"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f5202b821bd2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f70a89a52d13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114020", "c": "308", "s": "0501", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
