  ('medical-tech-moex-01962', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有  關肝素抗性（heparin resistance）之現象，下列敘述何者最適當？', '["肝  素被血小板第四因子（PF-4）吸附", "利  用低劑量肝素才可達到APTT標的範圍（target level）", "病  人antithrombin濃度太高而誘發", "病  人出現自體免疫抗體"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f5202b821bd2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f70a89a52d13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114020", "c": "308", "s": "0501", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
