  ('medical-tech-moex-01964', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有  關肝素所引發的血小板低下（heparin-induced thrombocytopenia, HIT），下列敘述何者最適當？', '["血  栓生成是HIT常見且風險性較高的臨床症狀", "可  用warfarin替代肝素來治療病人", "使  用低分子量肝素（low-molecular weight heparin）治療時仍須嚴密監控，主要是因其引起HIT的發生率 與傳統肝素（unfractionated heparin）相似", "主  要是由於血小板所釋出的PF3與肝素形成具抗原性的複合體而誘發抗血小板抗體所導致"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f5202b821bd2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f70a89a52d13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114020", "c": "308", "s": "0501", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-01965', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有  關Bethesda assay的敘述，下列何者最適當？', '["用  於定量檢測血漿中之anti-factor VIII antibodies或inhibitor", "在  Nijmegen修正方法（Nijmegen modification）中，是以pH 7.4的imidazole緩衝液與病人血漿進行 1：1混合", "一  個Bethesda單位（BU）是指可以完全中和一個單位（U）的factor VIII活性的抗體量", "檢  測步驟是須將病人之檢體與試劑混合後於室溫反應兩個小時"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f5202b821bd2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f70a89a52d13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114020", "c": "308", "s": "0501", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 48, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-01966', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有  關巨核細胞（MK）之細胞骨架與血小板生合成過程之間的相關性，下列敘述何者最適當？', '["M K中胞器的分布主要是由波形蛋白（vimentin）負責調控", "S pectrin-actin是形成和維持MK中DMS（demarcation system）所不可或缺的細胞骨架", "F -actin藉由解開DMS（demarcation system）的纏繞而拉長proplatelet，為成熟血小板的裂解做準備", "一  個MK可產生10000～50000顆血小板"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f5202b821bd2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f70a89a52d13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114020", "c": "308", "s": "0501", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 49, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
